IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User jorrifransen@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mutt/mb_pass.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Bin"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
